        "text": "16. If 2,470 is obtained as an interest in 4 years and 4 months at the rate of 3% per annum simple interest rate in bank deposit, how much amount was deposited in ?\n(A) 17,000\n(B) 18,000\n(C) 19,000\n(D) 20,000",
