        "id": "q35",
        "text": "35. If f(y) = 1/(1+y) and g(y) = (y+1)/y then fog(y)=\n(A) y/(2y+1)\n(B) 2y/(y+1)\n(C) (2y+1)/y\n(D) (y+1)/y",
