        "text": "46. Suresh started walking 4 km west from his office. Then he turned right and walked 2 km. Again he turned right and walked 2 km to reach his house. In which direction is Suresh's house from his office?\n(A) South\n(B) South-East\n(C) North-West\n(D) East",
